<div class="container mt-5">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-md-8">
            <div class="jumbotron">
                <h1 class="display-4 text-center">Privacy Policy</h1>
                <p class="lead text-center">At ITTS "O.Belluzzi L.da Vinci", we are committed to protecting the privacy and security of our students, parents, and visitors. This privacy policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard personal information gathered through our website, events, and communication channels.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-md-8">
            <div class="card mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2>Information We Collect:</h2>
                    <ul class="list-unstyled">
                        <li>
                            <h5>Personal Information:</h5>
                            <p>We may collect personal information such as names, email addresses, phone numbers, and mailing addresses when provided voluntarily by students, parents, or visitors for purposes such as event registration, newsletter subscriptions, or inquiries.</p>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <h5>Usage Information:</h5>
                            <p>We may collect non-personal information about the usage of our website, including IP addresses, browser types, and pages visited, to analyze trends, improve user experience, and administer the site effectively.</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2>How We Use Your Information:</h2>
                    <ul class="list-unstyled">
                        <li>
                            <h5>Communication:</h5>
                            <p>We may use the information provided to respond to inquiries, send important updates, newsletters, event invitations, and other relevant communications related to school activities and initiatives.</p>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <h5>Improvement of Services:</h5>
                            <p>We may use aggregated data to analyze trends, track user interactions, and enhance our website content, layout, and functionality to better serve our community.</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

<div class="card mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2>Protection of Information:</h2>
                    <p>We implement appropriate security measures to protect against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction of personal information collected through our website and other channels. We restrict access to personal information to authorized personnel only, who are required to maintain the confidentiality of such information.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2>Third-Party Disclosure:</h2>
                    <p>We do not sell, trade, or transfer personal information to third parties without consent unless required by law or to protect the rights, property, or safety of ITTS "O.Belluzzi L.da Vinci" and its community.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2>Your Choices:</h2>
                    <p>You have the right to review, update, or request the deletion of your personal information by contacting us directly. You may choose to opt-out of receiving promotional emails or newsletters by following the unsubscribe instructions provided in the communication.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2>Policy Updates:</h2>
                    <p>We reserve the right to update this privacy policy periodically to reflect changes in our practices or legal requirements. We encourage you to review this policy periodically for any updates. By using our website and providing personal information, you consent to the collection, use, and disclosure of information in accordance with this privacy policy.</p>
                    <p>If you have any questions or concerns about our privacy practices, please contact us at +00 513 7384551.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>